---
title: Crispy Parm Chicken and Herby Mash with Buttered Peas
description: There's nothing quite like a delicious, elegant meal that lands on the table in under 30 mins! We've paired crispy, cheesy baked chicken with a mountain of silky dill-garlic mashed potatoes for a show-stopping weeknight wonder.
